page.html:
• Rhythm game player since 2009. Games I played:
  • Donkey Konga
    DDR Mario Mix
    Dance!online (SDO)
    Stepmania
    Debut Online (Korea)
    O2Jam (Private Server)
    Guitar Hero (Phase Shift on PC)
    R2beat (Korea)
    MStar (Korea & Thailand)
    Lunatic Rave 2 (w/ Beatmania controller)
    AstroRanger (Korea)


Main !mania 4K player, 6 years of experience on Stepmania. Feel free to add me for advices and tips to improve your skills in 4K.
Actually practicing 7K on osu and O2Jam (V3 private server).

Thanks to T h X, _Gezo_ & kasky21 for supporter gifts. ♥

3rd place on the SOFT Free for all 4K Tournament. Thanks for the amazing trip Halogen- !
Leaded France to top 6 best team in the world at the MWC 4K 2016. Proud of my team, we did a great job.
Winner of the M4F: Mania French Frog 4K Tournament. Amazing job Xeostyle & Musty
Reached the semifinals of the MWC 7K 2017 being the only European team to reach the brackets. Very proud.
